divs: Sighting DetailsToday my fiance said check out how much they're spraying us! This is amazing....the most and closest chemtrails I've seen. I have more photos and longer videos. I clipped one video...check out when I scan past the house...at about 6 seconds in the corner are 2 objects that fly away in an unusual way...not a plane, helicopter, or weather balloon....crazy, I didn't notice them until I watched the video. Maryland Heights, MO around 4pm Central time, looking east.
